channel.title: Looking for a new Axoloti core for sale
channel.description:
I have been trying to get an Axoloti core for about a year and a half now and I can't seem to see them in stock ever, maybe production is over, I hope not. Is anyone willing to sell me a new Axoloti core ill pay shipping and the retail price + ill go up 10$ if you want. I live in the U.S.A.
Thank you

item.title: Looking for a new Axoloti core for sale

item.description:
